## Comparison
Method | Surface | Medium | scatter 
---- |:----:|:----:|:----:
PT   | Any | Any | Multiple
Naive NEE  | - | - | multiple 
[Walter09] | Smooth Dielectric | yes | single
[Walter09]_ext | Smooth Dielectric | yes | single
MNEE | rough dielectric | no/SDS | "single"
SNEE | rough dielectric | yes | multiple
MVNEE| no | yes |

